      "lib": "worklib",
      "view": "schematic"
    },
    "note": "Authentic CInExport of follower3 with port markers: IPORT (parallel, 0 A), VPORT1 (series, CL=1p load branch), VPORT2 (series, MN1 drain/supply branch). acm=1 on VIN/IPORT and CL's capacitance (from OP data) are netlister/OP-sourced, not hand-edited. psf/ = gain run (VIN excited, VPORT branch currents saved), psf_z/ = 1 A injection run (IPORT excited), xf.xf in both."
  },
  "top": "tb_follower3",
  "ground": [
    "0",
    "gnd!"
  ],
